verbose_text: Moreover, the protein levels of TLR4 and the phosphorylation levels of IkappaBalpha and NF-kappaB p65 proteins were also upregulated in the BRL44408 + tizanidine group compared with the saline + tizanidine group, indicating that the TLR4 / NF-kappaB signaling was activated when pretreated with BRL44408 in SNI rats (XREF_FIG).
